original_title: Shooting reported at night club in Kiribathgoda
original_body_lines: A shooting has taken place inside a night club at Gala Junction in Kiribathgoda at around 02.30 a.m. early this morning (18).
Police said that around 06 shots had been fired, and that however no one was reported injured in the incident.
Kiribathgoda Police and the Police Special Task Force (STF) have launched an investigation into the incident.
